manifest_description.message: The easiest and most effective way to locate a malicious or buggy extension.

ui_manual.message: This extension is used to assist in locating malicious or buggy extensions. After you click the Start button, the following steps will be performed.

ui_manual_step2.message: It is up to you to manually test if the target extension is still running, and this extension will further narrow the search based on your feedback.

ui_manual_step3.message: Cycle through steps 1 and 2 above until only one extension remains.

ui_exclusion_description.message: Exclude extensions that you do not want to disable.

dialog_confirm.message: Please test manually if the corresponding extension is still running and select the corresponding option according to the result.
